@HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### 开发测试 Token
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/dev-token
Accept: application/json

### 获取卡片列表
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
Accept: application/json

### 获取卡片列表（按状态筛选）
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards?status=todo&sort=updatedAt&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>

### 创建卡片
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试知识卡片",
  "sourceText": "这是一段原文摘录",
  "summary": "这是摘要",
  "sourceUrl": "https://example.com",
  "tags": ["AI", "Python"]
}

### 更新卡片
PATCH {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "summary": "更新后的摘要",
  "status": "done"
}

### 归档卡片
PATCH {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}/archive
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>

### 删除卡片
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>

### 获取用户信息
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer <你的Token>
